metadata.name: Key to the Neighborhood
metadata.description:
The Keys to the Neighborhood is a collection of 500 NFTs. These will grant you access to be one of the first to Mint Our Neighborhood NFTs. The keys will give you first come minting with all of Our Neighborhood Collections. The keys aren't just a simple “Whitelist” token, there is utility yet to be unveiled!! 

These keys grant you access to Our Neighborhood NFTs. These will be needed for future programs...
